  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1071">
<l>makkaḷē pōlvar kayava ravaraṉṉa</l>
<l>voppāri yāṅkaṇṭa til</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The base resemble men perfectly (as regards form) and we have not seen such (exact) resemblance (among any other species).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
